Selected Families and Individuals of British Royalty

Prince John William of Orange Friso [Parents] was born in 1686. He died in 1711. He married Mary Louise in 1709.

Mary Louise was born in 1688. She died in 1765. She married Prince John William of Orange Friso in 1709.

They had the following children:

M i Prince William IV of Orange was born in 1711. He died in 1751. F ii Charlotte Amalia was born in 1710. She died in 1777.

Prince William V of Orange [Parents] was born in 1748. He died in 1806. He married Wilhelmine.

Wilhelmine [Parents] was born in 1751. She died in 1820. She married Prince William V of Orange.

They had the following children:

F i Frederica was born in 1770. She died in 1819. M ii King William I of Netherlands was born on 24 Aug 1772. He died on 12 Dec 1843. M iii Frederick was born in 1774. He died in 1799.

Frederick I King of Prussia was born on 11 Jul 1657 in Konigsberg. He died on 25 Feb 1713 in Berlin. He married Sophia Charlotte on 8 Oct 1684 in Herrenhausen.

Other marriages:

, Elizabeth Henrietta of Hesse-Cassel

, Sophia Louise of Mecklenburg

Sophia Charlotte [Parents] was born on 20 Oct 1668 in Schloss Iburg. She died on 1 Feb 1705 in Hanover. She was buried in Berlin Cathedral. She married Frederick I King of Prussia on 8 Oct 1684 in Herrenhausen.

They had the following children:

M i Frederick Augustus was born in 1685. He died in 1686. M ii Son (stillborn) died . M iii Frederick William I King of Prussia was born on 14 Aug 1688. He died on 31 May 1740.

Frederick V King of Denmark [Parents] was born on 31 Mar 1723 in Copenhagen. He died on 14 Jan 1766 in Christiansborg. He married Juliana Maria on 8 Jul 1752 in Frederiksborg.

Other marriages:

Hanover, Louisa

Juliana Maria was born on 4 Sep 1729 in Wolfenbuttel. She died on 10 Oct 1796 in Fredensborg. She married Frederick V King of Denmark on 8 Jul 1752 in Frederiksborg.

They had the following children:

M i Frederick was born in 1753. He died in 1805.

Christian VI King of Denmark [Parents] died . He married Sophie Magdalene on 7 Aug 1721.

Sophie Magdalene was born on 28 Nov 1700. She died on 27 May 1770 in Christiansborg. She married Christian VI King of Denmark on 7 Aug 1721.

They had the following children:

M i Frederick V King of Denmark was born on 31 Mar 1723. He died on 14 Jan 1766. F ii Louise was born in 1726. She died in 1756.

Gustaf III King of Sweden was born in 1746. He died in 1792. He married Sophia Magdalena in 1766.

Sophia Magdalena [Parents] was born in 1746. She died in 1813. She married Gustaf III King of Sweden in 1766.

Elector William I of Hesse-Cassel was born in 1743. He died in 1821. He married Caroline in 1763.

Caroline [Parents] was born in 1747. She died in 1820. She married Elector William I of Hesse-Cassel in 1763.

Prince Alexander of Bulgaria [Parents] was born in 1857. He died in 1893. He married Johanna Loisinger in 1889.

Johanna Loisinger [Parents] was born in 1865. She died in 1951. She married Prince Alexander of Bulgaria in 1889.

Francis Joseph [Parents] was born in 1861. He died in 1924. He married Anna of Montenegro Princess.

Anna of Montenegro Princess died . She married Francis Joseph.

Louis III of Hesse Grand Duke [Parents] was born in 1806. He died in 1877. He married Princess Mathilde in 1833.

Other marriages:

, Magdalen of Hochstadten

Princess Mathilde [Parents] was born in 1813. She died in 1862. She married Louis III of Hesse Grand Duke in 1833.
